# Card 卡片

## 代码演示
+++
--- demo ---
#### 设置背景图
``` jsx
import { Card } from 'zeus'
class CardWithBackgroundDemo extends React.Component {
  render(){
    return (
      <Card
        imgSrc="http://ali.image.hellorf.com/images/1b90734b946e92a5c24738bde66879f5.jpeg"
        title="一张可爱的卡片"
      />
    )
  }
} 
```

+++
--- demo ---
#### 不同形态的卡片
卡片有三种不同的形式，分别是card, picture 和 atlas。
``` jsx
import { Card } from 'zeus'
class CardWithOperatorDemo extends React.Component {
  render(){
    return (
      <div>
        <div>
          <Card
            type="atlas"
            title="我是标题啊"
            subTitle="此文案"
            imgSrc="http://ali.image.hellorf.com/images/1b90734b946e92a5c24738bde66879f5.jpeg"
          />
        </div>

        <div style={{marginTop: 16}}>
          <Card
            type="card"
            title="我是标题啊"
            subTitle="此文案"
            imgSrc="http://ali.image.hellorf.com/images/1b90734b946e92a5c24738bde66879f5.jpeg"
          />
        </div>

        <div style={{marginTop: 16}}>
          <Card
            type="picture"
            title="我是标题啊"
            subTitle="此文案"
            imgSrc="http://ali.image.hellorf.com/images/1b90734b946e92a5c24738bde66879f5.jpeg"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    )
  }
} 
```

